.io/zh/story/%E5%BF%8F%E6%82%94/</guid><description>惭愧心 一念忏悔超八万大劫 一切劫为一念</description><dc:creator>Om</dc:creator><category>视频</category><category>禅</category><category>忏悔</category><category>韦陀菩萨</category><category>故事</category></item><item><title>了凡与禅</title><link>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/story/%E4%BA%86%E5%87%A1%E4%B8%8E%E4%BA%91%E8%B0%B7%E7%A6%85%E5%B8%88/</link><pubDate>Sun, 10 Apr 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:modified>Sun, 10 Apr 2022 00:00:00 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/story/%E4%BA%86%E5%87%A1%E4%B8%8E%E4%BA%91%E8%B0%B7%E7%A6%85%E5%B8%88/</guid><description>云谷禅师 天台小止观 云谷乃禅师的号，其法名为“法会”，明代憨山德清曾经撰有《云谷大师传》。大师早有异志，十九岁便开始行脚参方，遍访名师问道，于</description><dc:creator>Om</dc:creator><category>禅</category><category>佛</category><category>故事</category></item><item><title>定慧之路</title><link>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E5%BE%85%E5%AE%9A/%E5%AE%9A%E6%85%A7%E4%B9%8B%E8%B7%AF/</link><pubDate>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:modified>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E5%BE%85%E5%AE%9A/%E5%AE%9A%E6%85%A7%E4%B9%8B%E8%B7%AF/</guid><description>学佛修行路线图 link 正文 定慧之路 致光法师讲述 明至居士笔录 这条定慧之路，你若曾经走过，何必猜想我是谁！ 我本无我，常漂流生死海，何必问我在哪里？ 不是</description><dc:creator>Om</dc:creator><category>定慧之路</category><category>广超法师</category><category>禅</category><category>止</category><category>观</category><category>待考证</category><category>佛</category><category>南传</category></item></channel></rss>